@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}


<div class="d-grid gap-2">
    <div class="card rounded-3 ">
		<div class="card-body shadow-lg d-grid gap-2 col mx-auto">
				<h1 class="text-center display-1 ">
					<span class="text-center rounded-pill badge bg-warning text-uppercase text-primary text-opacity-75 shadow-lg">
						@ViewData["Title"]
						</span>
				</h1>
				<p></p>
<h2> Rizal Technological University Event Management System</h2>

<p>Effective Date: May 1, 2023 - May 1, 2024</p>

			<p>RTU values the privacy of its users and is committed to protecting their personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how personal information is collected, used, and disclosed through RTU's event management system, which is accessible via <a href="https://rtuems.rtu.rtu.ph">https://rtuems.rtu.edu.ph</a>.</p>
			<h2>1. Personal Information Collected</h2>
			<p>Personal information is collected from users when they register for an event or make a reservation. This may include their name, email address, phone number, student ID number, and other relevant details.</p>
			<h2>2. Use of Personal Information</h2>
			<p>Personal information collected is used to:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Confirm registration or reservation</li>
				<li>Provide event details and updates</li>
				<li>Respond to inquiries</li>
				<li>Improve the event management system</li>
			</ul>
			<h2>3. Disclosure of Personal Information</h2>
			<p>Personal information may be disclosed to third-party service providers who assist in providing the event management system. Personal information may also be disclosed when required by law or to protect legal rights.</p>
			<h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
			<p>Personal information is retained only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, and as required by law.</p>
			<h2>5. Security of Personal Information</h2>
			<p>Reasonable measures are taken to protect personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>
			<h2>6. User Rights</h2>
			<p>Users have the right to access and correct their personal information, and to request its deletion. To exercise these rights, users can contact RTU at <a href="mailto:rtuems@rtu.edu.ph">rtuems@rtu.edu.ph</a>.</p>
			<h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
			<p>RTU's event management system is not intended for children under 13. Personal information is not knowingly collected from children under 13. Parents or guardians who believe their child has provided personal information can contact RTU at <a href="mailto:rtuems@rtu.edu.ph">rtuems@rtu.edu.ph</a>.</p>
			<h2>8. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
			<p>RTU may update this Privacy Policy. The effective date at the top of this page indicates the date when the policy was last revised. Continued use of the event management system after changes signifies acceptance of the revised policy.</p>
			<p>If there are any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, users can contact RTU at <a href="mailto:rtuems@rtu.edu.ph">rtuems@rtu.edu.ph</a>.</p>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
